data.description: Calling all Investors! Dont miss out on this one! Location is EVERYTHING! This original 1958 ranch 3 bedroom, 1 bath home has so much to offer.  .44 acres lot on the main Rock Quarry Road. Here is your opportunity to explore a property with close proximity to Downtown Raleigh, Coastal Credit Union Coastal Park, restaurants, shopping amenities and so much more. What a great opportunity to renovate or build new with new construction nearby.  This may be what you've been looking for that's in need of your creative inspiration!
